      "title": "Protestors break the first line of barricades near Parliament",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Hundreds of protestors have broken the first line of barricades set up outside the Parliament while forces are firing tear gas to disperse the crowds.",
        "At party leaders' meeting held a short while ago, security forces discussed if force should be used to protect the Parliament, however this request was turned down by the leaders present."
